process.name: Get ReAssignable Tasks by Multiple Criteria

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select lt.TASK_ID as TaskID, LP."NAME" as ApplicationName, LUX.USER_NAME as UserName, LUGX.DESCRIPTION as groupName, LT.SUBJECT as TaskSubject, LT.ACTIVITY_NAME as ActivityName, LT.BPD_INSTANCE_ID as InstanceID, LT.EXECUTION_STATUS as ExecutionStatus, LTSC."NAME" as status from lsw_project lp, lsw_snapshot ls, lsw_usr_xref lux, lsw_task lt, LSW_TASK_STATUS_CODES ltsc, lsw_usr_grp_xref lugx where lp.project_id = ls.PROJECT_ID and lt.user_id = lux.user_id(+) and LT.snapshot_id = LS.SNAPSHOT_ID and LTSC.STATUS_VALUE = LT.STATUS and LT."GROUP_ID" = LUGX."GROUP_ID"(+) and lt.status not in (32) and lt.activity_task_type = 1 and (LT.EXECUTION_STATUS != 1 or LT.EXECUTION_STATUS is null) and (UPPER(LUX.USER_NAME) like ? or UPPER(LT.SUBJECT) like ? or UPPER(LT.ACTIVITY_NAME) like ? or LT.TASK_ID = ? or LT.BPD_INSTANCE_ID = ? or UPPER(lp.name) like ? or UPPER(lugx.description) like ? ) order by lt.rcvd_datetime desc
